{"tid":2294430,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"大家客觀討論吓神作鬼滅之刃既成功之道係乜？","createTime":"2020-11-21T04:25:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-24T11:13:46.000Z","uid":241151,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"e12a3ae6bdfffe6312b8627794dc7363c521ebb1","tid":2294430,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:25:54.000Z","msg":"我認同係用簡單直接既王道方式去寫個故事，以往真係冇乜作品會咁做，鬼滅之刃可以講係創先河 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fe5fc4c6ef1e38fb43fd3d9e1250d8bd0bae0c6","tid":2294430,"uid":46389,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"jump出盡奶力谷人氣"},{"pid":"e87a6b2a21625ce8f5d2a390f428f4d3ff9d364b","tid":2294430,"uid":62318,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"ufo 劇情唔拖"},{"pid":"e2a353acf71b58070346106a433d010776327e90","tid":2294430,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e87a6b2a21625ce8f5d2a390f428f4d3ff9d364b","tid":2294430,"uid":62318,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:28:41.000Z","msg":"ufo 劇情唔拖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:34:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce27d21360d5679efbd133ce405348469d852346","tid":2294430,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"4fe5fc4c6ef1e38fb43fd3d9e1250d8bd0bae0c6","tid":2294430,"uid":46389,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:27:30.000Z","msg":"jump出盡奶力谷人氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:34:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aa82e06551820a4fc8c6ef96912dec333ca01a9","tid":2294430,"uid":299548,"like":5,"dislike":24,"score":-19,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-21T04:35:19.000Z","msg":"贏在玩刀 有刀劍神域嘅影子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/asset